{"tid":528164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"Long d巴絲求取暖","createTime":"2018-01-13T13:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T13:49:30.000Z","uid":136940,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7e7e4d3072f495ea087763d208f431bf9934e6","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"同男朋友long d幾個月<br />\n佢好似成日都好忙生活好充實 而我係香港就悶到死 唔係翻學翻工就摺係屋企<br />\n開始愈嚟愈少溝通 whatsapp每日淨係早晨早抖幾句 FaceTime更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我好悶 一停低就會諗起佢 好掛住佢<br />\n有好多野想同佢講同佢分享 但可能大家生活圈子唔同 又有時差 隔好耐先覆又或者對方又未必想知 <br />\n硬係覺得佢已經無以前咁愛我了 定係自己亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過仲有好耐先有得見面<br />\n總之個感覺就好難受 有無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先開錯台 再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4705768aa7c8a9bc1d2c4ec835eff802cabb311e","tid":528164,"uid":1952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"取咩暖呀 好難呀真係<br />\n以後唔敢再試<br />\n手已分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8001575e8abc908974454c59af26727560cd768","tid":528164,"uid":129592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:47:35.000Z","msg":"係香港認識左佢<br />\n以為曖昩過<br />\n以為只要繼續落去就會一齊 之後等佢返<br />\n結果唔好講等乜等乜<br />\n根本一齊唔到<br />\n佢最近都有新對象<br />\n又或者可能我從來唔係佢對象<br />\n是我敏感 誤會戀愛降臨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以照取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d5b0cb94264e10fd75dfd67141f297bfdb7df7","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港認識左佢<br />\n以為曖昩過<br />\n以為只要繼續落去就會一齊 之後等佢返<br />\n結果唔好講等乜等乜<br />\n根本一齊唔到<br />\n佢最近都有新對象<br />\n又或者可能我從來唔係佢對象<br />\n是我敏感 誤會戀愛降臨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以照取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊緊都有好多變數<br />\n更何況無一齊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢首歌我都日loop夜loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcfa004a64397f441c1d4ed05001d2b2e27f073","tid":528164,"uid":115584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:00:17.000Z","msg":"帽事嘅<br />\n利申：LD左5年都係要散"},{"pid":"8d59683f2d6cc7e89d997a22a92fb865551fa446","tid":528164,"uid":115584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:01:23.000Z","msg":"LD講commitment 大家唔肯付出個心都冇用"},{"pid":"6b479090988dc32bc33d642c9fdd0e39080622da","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>取咩暖呀 好難呀真係<br />\n以後唔敢再試<br />\n手已分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為自己識到佢可以同佢一齊係用曬我一生所有幸運換翻黎 覺得自己太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1dcfac512006df8aecf7acb6a70bb310859551","tid":528164,"uid":9335,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:03:33.000Z","msg":"不如留個tg傾下？"},{"pid":"02716a6277051b38a21c8a9477167fc1f0f77614","tid":528164,"uid":9335,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0a1dcfac512006df8aecf7acb6a70bb310859551","tid":528164,"uid":9335,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:03:33.000Z","msg":"不如留個tg傾下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/tg123321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftg123321&d=O%2BsyYLFTxwcZnUDajpZneTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2744d519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tg123321</a>"},{"pid":"cfc339a70779b91355792c21b2f311c13aa81d9e","tid":528164,"uid":129592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52d5b0cb94264e10fd75dfd67141f297bfdb7df7","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港認識左佢<br />\n以為曖昩過<br />\n以為只要繼續落去就會一齊 之後等佢返<br />\n結果唔好講等乜等乜<br />\n根本一齊唔到<br />\n佢最近都有新對象<br />\n又或者可能我從來唔係佢對象<br />\n是我敏感 誤會戀愛降臨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以照取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊緊都有好多變數<br />\n更何況無一齊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢首歌我都日loop夜loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:10:33.000Z","msg":"未一齊 零感情基礎<br />\n兩個都忙 少溝通<br />\n佢條件好 好多人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衰女講句 連我自己中間忙都淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係宜家覺得好酸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇呀 咁咪做long d朋友囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果佢冇鐘意嘅人 可能我都會唔死心<br />\n既然佢都有鐘意嘅人 咁我都冇野做到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打要加油<br />\n係咪long d都好 遇到個可以相愛嘅人真係唔容易啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實難架 你冇咩忙係好事<br />\n就算對方忙 至少佢知道你一直係佢身邊<br />\n兩個都忙都唔主動<br />\n就好快會完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2ffde9e7cecce2f25275835a09e24534843d6f","tid":528164,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303c5938854fbff239688564cc34b36c4fbda082","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗諗下其實佢無左我 對佢黎講都無影響 佢既生活都一樣咁開心充實 只係我一個人唔開心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd69ba6af22861a3236bbd5f13986aef130cfc4","tid":528164,"uid":112987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3532c219425391706ebc4333fe1fd446dac3eca0","tid":528164,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗如果係真既話我會完全崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2489414cf3523a453a64968228ad25d3d930265","tid":528164,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd69ba6af22861a3236bbd5f13986aef130cfc4","tid":528164,"uid":112987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"So true<br />\n我係因為咁而散左<br />\n樓主既情況應該都差唔多散"},{"pid":"f8ada0c1ebfff154408f0eb38f27aff82e15eaef","tid":528164,"uid":91173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23b1fef851648f1c3985bbb2f214c5073bbdae7","tid":528164,"uid":143307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"遠距離要好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油呀...努力撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14563a45bd67510091645edafbd34bbc6fe2238c","tid":528164,"uid":118127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"唉...我呢排都因為long d散左..<br />\n女方話無左以前對我既個種熱情....<br />\n分個陣，我又好瀟灑話咁你都考慮得咁清楚，咁我點挽救都無用..<br />\n<br />\n依家覺得好唔甘心無盡力挽救過...我諗緊專唔專登過去試一次挽救....<br />\n<br />\n去唔去好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e3483742fd3f5405742459a3e7dd10d0298a41","tid":528164,"uid":148857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2489414cf3523a453a64968228ad25d3d930265","tid":528164,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd69ba6af22861a3236bbd5f13986aef130cfc4","tid":528164,"uid":112987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"So true<br />\n我係因為咁而散左<br />\n樓主既情況應該都差唔多散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"我也是同樣成功分手既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌佢老母話好悶好寂寞所以去媾女"},{"pid":"abc126939c3dcfb8b5a9148efd601c6764baaf31","tid":528164,"uid":76103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  long d真係好難，大家都好有心維繫嘅，不過始終都係有好多conflict，而佢係外國又有好多壓力，佢話好攰，同我一齊好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等緊佢開心翻之後理翻我，不過其實唔知係咪自己呃自己佢一定會留係自己身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個人都好唔開心，呢幾日成日偷偷地喊但唔想比人知，好灰個人"},{"pid":"1e11880ea6447a930a3224ed0cd8975397353df3","tid":528164,"uid":20736,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"我條女係香港東<br />\n我係新界西<br />\n每次都搭好耐車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal